column2: This sheet contains the test cases for validating all User functions, including login, registration, viewing menu items, managing the shopping cart (add/update/remove), and placing orders. The objective is to ensure that all user-facing features work correctly, meet business rules, and interact with the system and database as expected.
Nguy?n Ph?m Hoàng Quân, Nguy?n Tr?n Qu?c Ti?n
